info: RLX Technology Inc., together with its subsidiaries, researchers, develops, manufactures, distributes, and sells e-vapor products in the People's Republic of China. It serves RELX branded partner stores and other retail outlets through distributors. The company was founded in 2018 and is based in Beijing, China. RLX Technology Inc. was formerly a subsidiary of Relx Inc.
19th Floor, Building 1 No. 10 South Chaoyang Park Avenue Chaoyang District
